txt.en: 'Good to see you [placeholder]. We are in need of some eggs here in Iridír to produce a much desired meal.\n\n'Can you travel to Shegdush and collect as many eggs as you find? Please also thin the numbers of chickens and boars in the area before it becomes a danger to others.'
Your mission is to travel to Shegdush and gather eggs and thin the numbers of chickens and boars in the area. Return with the scout to Setokúli with this report.
Your mission is to travel to Shegdush and gather food for the people of Iridír from the chickens and boars in the area.
'Wonderful! The eggs you have managed to gather will be put to great use for the meal. Please accept this reward for your troubles.'
There is no twist in this mission.
Your mission is to travel to Shegdush and gather food for the people of Iridír from the chickens and boars in the area.
Your mission is to travel to Shegdush and gather eggs and thin the numbers of chickens and boars in the area.\n\nSpeak to Setokúli to travel.
